{"tid":1791315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德福廣場由黨鐵擁有，由黨鐵作物業管理","createTime":"2019-12-20T16:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T04:40:23.000Z","uid":230104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"355a3754f6b5c528436f1051085ac9d916c4bb8f","tid":1791315,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/USKwBh8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUSKwBh8.png&h=82ffaaee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德福廣場（英語：Telford Plaza）是香港九龍九龍灣的大型購物商場之一，位於港鐵總部大樓、恒生中心和德福花園的下方。發展商為前地鐵公司（今港鐵公司）聯同合和集團及恒隆集團合組的德福發展有限公司（只負責一期）和新世界集團（只負責二期）。<span style=\"color: red;\">德福廣場現正由港鐵公司作物業管理</span>。1980-1997年間稱為德福商場，1997年後則稱為德福廣場，並分為一期及二期。一期商場已於1980年開幕，而二期商場於1997年12月6日開幕。當時由於九龍灣仍是一個工商業區，而觀塘至九龍灣一帶的工商業區仍以工業大廈為主，所以德福廣場當時可說是觀塘區，甚至東九龍唯一的大型商場。"},{"pid":"af047a539f6cb4ed06c0f8b53247df8a9bf29d7f","tid":1791315,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"唔怪得管理到班保安放D曱甴自出自入<br />\n<br />\n有D同情又一城"},{"pid":"d650d5344bf77a00fdb5fc7d415736b720b8b9d2","tid":1791315,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:56:35.000Z","msg":"玩完!"},{"pid":"d843d160b6e0096a8a9625595d6b44e83e80f98a","tid":1791315,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:57:09.000Z","msg":"12.21 1500 <br />\n光復元朗2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4686255e627c3a805557e6c489b016dac885a453","tid":1791315,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"以後咪撚去德福"},{"pid":"1bfe0baddfd146493f2492aa60b7ddb1de629445","tid":1791315,"uid":230104,"like